{"tid":1887031,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"事實上，口罩供應已經開始穩定，炒狗亦可以準備收皮。","createTime":"2020-02-19T09:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T08:55:48.000Z","uid":263038,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"295a2237f5834400699fba395ac8256f18c509a3","tid":1887031,"uid":263038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:39:32.000Z","msg":"各大連鎖鋪明顯地開始有穩定貨源<br />\n而部份民主派亦不斷班口罩返嚟畀大家<br />\n只要大家唔再同炒狗同藥房狗買炒價口罩<br />\n另外港豬們亦唔好再囤貨心態咁買口罩<br />\n口罩遲早會供過於求<br />\n嗰價就好快回復正常<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家就可以食住花生睇炒狗仆街</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f29c34e47f571aa89bfb1c1fa374397a69be3c37","tid":1887031,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"預過多一個月會變蟹貨"},{"pid":"90e538e7a3a4a21fab46f33ed6ddd5ddb927f1ca","tid":1887031,"uid":3122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"50蚊就叫穩定"},{"pid":"fa07dc29f248fed6f6d49482dad0dca3813adc58","tid":1887031,"uid":335883,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:42:12.000Z","msg":"睇定啲先 <br />\n宜家東南亞隨時蝗災到時可能有另一波炒賣"},{"pid":"36c82b000e20bbe8e04cbea8fddad2eb191787e5","tid":1887031,"uid":81045,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:48:48.000Z","msg":"依家到嘅貨全部都係倉底現貨<br />\n呢批完咗之後<br />\n要睇吓生產量係咪真係跟得上"},{"pid":"542500f76271d219fef947a819702804dfcf9119","tid":1887031,"uid":12994,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32e6ea1b29573ae4052a57725ed5a024f452146","tid":1887031,"uid":77222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:12:36.000Z","msg":"正唔洗買炒價啦"},{"pid":"9e04d334743492e217857faf42e8e157511f4c36","tid":1887031,"uid":316255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"542500f76271d219fef947a819702804dfcf9119","tid":1887031,"uid":12994,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T13:53:26.000Z","msg":"agger依排到貨<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3274f94a0b0349d920be7edef8a359452578b15c","tid":1887031,"uid":61745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"542500f76271d219fef947a819702804dfcf9119","tid":1887031,"uid":12994,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:43:23.000Z","msg":"早排咁缺個個周圍搵，d貨夜過來就係呢排到，好多地方禁晒運口罩出國，呢批貨賣晒又打回原形。"},{"pid":"6c546726a786208f2709d6b284b236236febf63b","tid":1887031,"uid":294413,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"復工計左未<br />\n中國日本特別行政區大爆發計左未"},{"pid":"1c5b7f92327757706594bbfb6d64858044c19bde","tid":1887031,"uid":350235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T19:38:24.000Z","msg":"如果真係口罩供應趨穩定，確實係好事。<br />\n不過睇數據就好難樂觀。爆發疫情前每日產能4000萬個，一半係内地，三成幾係日本。全球就算產能喺兩個月内升10倍，都係4億個每日，對比WHO宣稱口罩需求暴增100倍，隨時有15億人每日都需要口罩，區區4億恐怕係杯水車薪。宜家内地自己都唔夠，日本市面無貨，如果日本都爆發疫情，全球兩大口罩生產國（過八成產能）都自顧不暇，香港嘅口罩供貨只會雪上加霜。<br />\n再者，其他國家可能都相繼禁運口罩。"},{"pid":"d46136e3892dc2296bcd0da4518d9dbd37ccf453","tid":1887031,"uid":341865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90e538e7a3a4a21fab46f33ed6ddd5ddb927f1ca","tid":1887031,"uid":3122,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"50蚊就叫穩定"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T01:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁你俾心機等到疫情完啦"},{"pid":"8b9317187296e640497ddf8e7e4f9ef05e35f252","tid":1887031,"uid":3122,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d46136e3892dc2296bcd0da4518d9dbd37ccf453","tid":1887031,"uid":341865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi